cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.GR 

This paper deals with computer vision and robotics, specifically the task of 6D multi-object pose estimation in cluttered scenarios. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also makes use of reinforcement learning, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) or cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper deals with robotics applications, which could place it in cs.RO (Robotics and Control) or cs.GR (Graphics).
